{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"htmlAst":{"type":"element","tagName":"div","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"grid","properties":{"background":"magenta-20","className":["background--header","background--thinking"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","md":"4"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Enterprise Design Thinking"}]}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Design thinking shouldn’t be controversial—it’s simply the idea that everyone on a team should be focused on their users, first and foremost."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We built on that idea, adding strategies, tactics and activities to create a framework that uniquely scales design thinking across teams of all shapes and sizes, whether they are co-located or widely dispersed."}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"8","offset_lg":"4","md":"4"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"grid","properties":{"background":"gray-10"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Principles"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"12","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The foundational elements"},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"of our approach"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","offset_lg":"4","border":"true","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A focus on user outcomes"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Who are you designing for, and what do they need?"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"We measure success by how well we fulfill human needs. Our users are more than just the people we make for, they’re our partners in design."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/design-website/deploy-previews/506/think_circle-6f67851700b40a720fa4090201d4c7b8.svg","alt":"It's a circle."},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","border":"true","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Restless reinvention"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"When’s the last time you rethought what you’re making?"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"Everything is a prototype. Being essential—and staying essential—requires a continuous conversation with our users and clients, responding to their changing needs through rapid prototyping and constant iteration."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/design-website/deploy-previews/506/think-8faebeacfcd3c9125be8742f81f58e22.svg","alt":"Enterprise Design Thinking loop graphic."},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","border":"true","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Diverse empowered teams"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Do you have the right mix of makers?"}]},{"type":"text","value":" "},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"Diversity is the bedrock of a dynamic team. By empowering people with different skillsets, backgrounds and perspectives to bring their unique points of view to the table, we generate more breakthrough ideas faster."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/design-website/deploy-previews/506/think_3circles-8fc264780cb52abdfad95b81bd98669c.svg","alt":"Three circles stacked on top of each other."},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"grid","properties":{"background":"white"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Loop"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"12","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A process of rapid iteration"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","offset_lg":"4","border":"true","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Observe"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To drive meaningful outcomes for our users, we must first gain a deep understanding of the challenges they face.\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nBy constantly immersing ourselves in the worlds of our users, we ensure that our solutions always address real-world needs."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/design-website/deploy-previews/506/observe_loop-cd0d4e4d46edbb0f88404eeb7c6a2318.svg","alt":"Enterprise Design Thinking loop with an arrow on observe."},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","border":"true","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reflect"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Different people can interpret the same situation in very different ways.\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nComing together to reflect on our observations helps us synthesize and analyze findings, building a more nuanced understanding of our users across the team."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/design-website/deploy-previews/506/reflect_loop-dab9a0a542f19b9eb239e5a18c5a5ac2.svg","alt":"Enterprise Design Thinking loop with an arrow on reflect."},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","border":"true","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Make"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The only way to see an outcome is to make one—even if the idea isn’t fully baked yet.\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nRapid, low-fidelity prototyping allows us to simulate ideas and test hypotheses quickly and cheaply. The end result: solutions that are robust, effective, and battle-tested."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/design-website/deploy-previews/506/make_loop-24f678a8875be0424c1660b85fd4b036.svg","alt":"Enterprise Design Thinking loop with an arrow on make."},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"grid","properties":{"background":"gray-10"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Keys"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"12"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tactics for maintaining alignment"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","offset_lg":"4","border":"true","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hills"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hills are concise statements of\nthe goals we aim to help our users accomplish. By making these goals explicit and evaluating them regularly, we align teams around a single shared mission."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/design-website/deploy-previews/506/hills-9dbc717207806f7f14b8a831c6eac7eb.svg","alt":"It's a triangle."},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","border":"true","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Playbacks"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Playbacks are regular check-ins that bring users, stakeholders and teams together to tell stories and exchange feedback. They allow us to measure progress on a regular basis while uncovering and addressing any misalignment that may exist."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/design-website/deploy-previews/506/playbacks-c0d2c7f7bd6fc9faa3d84bca555c49ad.svg","alt":"It's a square."},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"4","border":"true","md":"5"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sponsor Users"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sponsor users are real-world users that provide teams with deep expertise and knowledge on the problems they’re facing. They are crucial to keeping us aligned with our users’ reality throughout the course of a project."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"/design-website/deploy-previews/506/sponsor_users-a3d14b36032bd16ce1733ff2aeaf441d.svg","alt":"It's an asterisk."},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"grid","properties":{"background":"gray-10"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"column","properties":{"lg":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"div","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"tile","properties":{"href":"https://www.ibm.com/design/thinking/","title":"Enterprise Design Thinking","feature":"true","feature_heading":"Explore our framework and start driving better, human-centered outcomes at any scale.","feature_background":"black"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"],"style":"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1312px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gats